## LayoutContext

File: `apps/backoffice-web/src/components/layout/LayoutContext.tsx`

```tsx
import { useLayout } from "../layout/LayoutContext";

function MyComponent() {
  const { sidebarCollapsed, toggleSidebar } = useLayout();
  // use sidebarCollapsed to adapt layout to sidebar width
}
```

Available anywhere inside `BackofficeLayout`.

---

## Adding a new route

1. Add the route in `apps/backoffice-web/src/App.tsx` inside the `<RequireAuth>` / `<BackofficeLayout>` block:

```tsx
<Route path="/my-new-page" element={<MyNewPage />} />
```

2. Add the corresponding `NavChild` in `navConfig.ts`.

Both steps are always needed together.

