## MegaMenuPanel

File: `apps/backoffice-web/src/components/layout/MegaMenuPanel.tsx`

- Automatically positioned flush to the right of the sidebar (accounts for collapsed state)
- Renders `module.sections` as a 2-column grid
- Dark bg-gray-900, active item highlighted in blue-600
- Only shown when the active module has `flyout: true` and the flyout is open

Do not render `MegaMenuPanel` manually — it is driven by `AppSidebar` state.

