## Sidebar color reference

| Element | Class |
|---|---|
| Sidebar background | `bg-gray-900` |
| Module row — inactive | `text-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-800` |
| Module row — active | `bg-gray-700 text-white font-medium` |
| Accordion sub-item — inactive | `text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-white` |
| Accordion sub-item — active | `bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium` |
| Separator | `bg-gray-700` |
| Collapse toggle | `text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-white` |
| MegaMenu section header | `bg-gray-800 text-gray-400` |
| MegaMenu item — active | `bg-blue-600 text-white` |
| Header background | `bg-gray-900 border-gray-700` |
